{"tid":1676501,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"主子今日絕完育","createTime":"2019-10-26T13:24:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T21:27:34.000Z","uid":100502,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"afce2e012090c4ddbf9a7eefaeb889e9c940412d","tid":1676501,"uid":100502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:24:51.000Z","msg":"我家主子今日絕完育.仔嚟嘅.佢好唔鐘意有嘢帶係身同埋困籠.但姑娘話要戴兩個星期頭套同困籠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢返到嚟好頹.有胃口食嘢.但就瘋狂想整甩個頭套同想出嚟.放出嚟又驚佢周圍跳整到傷口.真係好心痛.我可以做啲咩.可摸耳唔戴咁耐頭套<br />\n望住主子咁忍唔住喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8acb97b9858ca15ce8d86ca583f3442c43558f2","tid":1676501,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:25:08.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1ebc88124f3533ffd33746f095fbcccf864bade","tid":1676501,"uid":8500,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:27:10.000Z","msg":"你個仔割完包皮都要戴個外賣杯啦<br />\n係咁慘架啦"},{"pid":"a3e49345a300ea4ee57af009957c0c4c4deda4cf","tid":1676501,"uid":269681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:27:44.000Z","msg":"女仔 困左一日就放左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後DIY左件衫仔比佢著 姐住佢傷口"},{"pid":"1e1ad596891ce4a4497d7c44802ec033250f13ca","tid":1676501,"uid":100502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1ebc88124f3533ffd33746f095fbcccf864bade","tid":1676501,"uid":8500,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:27:10.000Z","msg":"你個仔割完包皮都要戴個外賣杯啦<br />\n係咁慘架啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:44:10.000Z","msg":"冇經驗..<br />\n男仔割完真係要戴外賣杯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gi